'''Narsacc Habitat''' was one of the six triangular luxury pods of [[Toryaz Station]]. It was 40 meters thick and 250 meters across, and connected to the main station by a 250 meter long spoke. It contained [[Kallebarth Way]] and [[Varganner Way]]. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], the meeting between [[Gilad Pellaeon/Legends|Gilad Pellaeon]] and [[Aidel Saxan]] took place on Narsacc Habitat.

